            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I think we discussed long ago adding a `exit` UI event, this has been requested by GUIs before. We have a `error_exit` event but it's not documented https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/29146 and seems unnecessarily limited. \n\nIf we are worried about back-compat we could simply document `error_exit` as also happening on a successful exit. @bfredl  ?\n\nRelated:\n\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/21843",
